room_title: Escape room "Aladdin: Quest for the Lamp" by Elite Escape Room in King of Prussia
room_description: The evil vizier has taken over town, and with no one to stop him you will need to step up to the job! You've heard rumblings of a magical genie sealed in a lamp that will grant you three wishes if you can get to it. The problem is, you're not sure where it is! Follow the clues, find the lamp, and save the village!
